[[Malay titles|Tun]] '''Mohammad Said bin Keruak''' (15 November 1925 – 17 November 1995)<ref>[http://ww2.sabah.gov.my/istana/Biodata%20%20Tun%20Mohd.%20Said%20bin%20Keruak.html Biodata Tun Mohd Said bin Keruak]</ref> was the fourth [[Chief Minister of Sabah|Chief Minister]] as well the seventh [[Yang di-Pertua Negeri|Governor]] of the Malaysian state of [[Sabah]].
