{{Infobox football biography | name = Syahrizal Syahbuddin | fullname = Syahrizal Syahbuddin | image = | height = {{convert|1.80|m|ftin|abbr=on}} | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1993|10|2}} | birth_place = [[Bireuën]], [[Indonesia]] | currentclub = [[Aceh United F.C.]] | clubnumber = 33 | position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]] | youthyears1 = 2008–2010 | youthclubs1 = Escuela Empoli | youthyears2 = 2011 | youthclubs2 = [[Sportivo Trinidense]] | youthyears3 = 2013 | youthclubs3 = [[Persija Jakarta U-21|Persija U-21]] | years1 = 2011 | clubs1 = [[Atlántida Sport Club|Atlántida]] | caps1 = 0 | goals1 = 0 | years2 = 2012–2013 | clubs2 = [[PSSB Bireun]] | caps2 = 26 | goals2 = 1 | years3 = 2013–2014 | clubs3 = [[Persija Jakarta]] | caps3 = 33 | goals3 = 0 | years4 = 2014–2016 | clubs4 = [[Mitra Kukar F.C.|Mitra Kukar]] | caps4 = 24 | goals4 = 0 | years5 = 2017 | clubs5 = [[Celebest F.C.|Celebest]] | caps5 = | goals5 = | years6 = 2018– | clubs6 = [[Aceh United F.C.|Aceh United]] | caps6 = 6 | goals6 = 0 | nationalyears1 = 2013–2014 | nationalteam1 = [[Indonesia national under-23 football team|Indonesia U23]] | nationalcaps1 = 3 | nationalgoals1 = 0 | pcupdate = 23:14, 13 December 2014 (UTC) | ntupdate = 13 July 2013 }} '''Syahrizal Syahbuddin'''<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/-syahrizal/281214/|title=syahrizal|website=soccerway}}</ref> (born in [[Bireuën]], Indonesia, October 2, 1993) is an [[Indonesia]]n footballer who currently plays for [[Aceh United F.C.]]<ref name="syakir dan syahrizal">{{cite web|url=http://klikkabar.com/2017/12/27/syakir-dan-syahrizal-merapat-ke-aceh-united/|title=Syakir dan Syahrizal Merapat ke Aceh United|website=klikkabar.com|accessdate=15 May 2018}}</ref> as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]]. He was the [[Expatriate footballers in Paraguay|first Indonesian footballer to play in Paraguay]].
== Club career == In December 2014, he joined Mitra Kukar<ref>{{cite web|title=Rahmat Affandi Dan Syahrizal Resmi Ke Mitra Kukar|url=http://www.bolaindo.com/2014/12/13/rahmat-affandi-dan-syahrizal-resmi-ke-mitra-kukar/|accessdate=13 December 2014|language=Indonesian|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20141213231555/http://www.bolaindo.com/2014/12/13/rahmat-affandi-dan-syahrizal-resmi-ke-mitra-kukar/|archivedate=13 December 2014|df=}}</ref>. In 2018, he joined [[Aceh United F.C.|Aceh United]]<ref name="syakir dan syahrizal"/>.
== International career == He made his debut for [[Indonesia national under-23 football team|Indonesia under-23 national team]] in friendly match against [[Singapore national under-23 football team|Singapore U-23]] on 13 July 2013 with score 1-0 for Singapore.
